{"tid":2080663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德法承諾政治及財政支援世衛　譚德塞稱正獲所需支持","createTime":"2020-06-26T14:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T15:55:13.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7c067cf7b46abc564719ebb17c3a56190284aef9","tid":2080663,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T14:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1534125_1_20200625212745.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1534125_1_20200625212745.jpg&h=4f7f9ff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚德塞在日內瓦的記者會上表示，組織正在獲得所需的財政和政治支持。（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n法國和德國表示，會在政治和財政上支援世界衛生組織，抗擊新型冠狀病毒疫情。世衛總幹事譚德塞表示，組織正在獲得所需的支持。<br />\n<br />\n美國是世衛最大的捐助國，2019年捐款超過4億美元，佔組織預算的約15%，但總統特朗普不滿世衛應對新型肺炎疫情的表現，上月揚言中斷與世衛的關係。<br />\n<br />\n德國衛生部長表示，國際社會現時需要一個比以往任何時候都要強大、透明和負責任的世衛組織，今年將向世衛撥款5億歐元捐助，是有記錄以來最多。法國則表示，將向世衛在里昂的一個研究中心撥款9000萬歐元，並會另外再捐贈5000萬歐元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534125-20200625.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534125-20200625.htm&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=0bfcd9d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534125-20200625.htm&h=64ae9ef9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534125-20200625.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cc67b9127eb1493abee4b94267b12e738c647af6","tid":2080663,"uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xKqSk6i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxKqSk6i.jpg&h=33f7bc52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e17ee3f208279d7cf111e82d45422bf7c4759ad8","tid":2080663,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:11:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪"},{"pid":"a95e1a3666ea4a2edcbeafb93dc10bd93b5f5f6f","tid":2080663,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:49:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"></span>"},{"pid":"bace43857cfdc63d7655d5e4f662699ffa150e76","tid":2080663,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:55:13.000Z","msg":"法德收皮啦屌你老母"}]}